text: Amir Hossein Hosseinzadeh (; born October 30, 2000) is an Iranian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Iranian club Saipa in the Persian Gulf Pro League. ==Club career== ===Saipa=== He made his debut for Saipa in 17th fixtures of 2018–19 Iran Pro League against Paykan while he substituted in for Arash Rezavand. ==References== Category:Living people Category:2000 births Category:Association football midfielders Category:Iranian footballers Category:Saipa F.C. players
